    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209860/extras/0d26e4b8d2b0049a7f3d95149d1075be.poster.avif?t=1737066645\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209860/extras/0d26e4b8d2b0049a7f3d95149d1075be.webm?t=1737066645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209860/extras/0d26e4b8d2b0049a7f3d95149d1075be.mp4?t=1737066645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Someone is trying to get in, and you need to stop him. Use alarms and whatever else you can to keep the intruder out. If you let your guard down, it’s game over for real.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209860/extras/6a8b0ad1f6d94fcf5eaf183e27a443ab.poster.avif?t=1737066645\" width=800 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209860/extras/6a8b0ad1f6d94fcf5eaf183e27a443ab.webm?t=1737066645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209860/extras/6a8b0ad1f6d94fcf5eaf183e27a443ab.mp4?t=1737066645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep an eye on the security cameras around your house. Someone's out there, and he's getting closer. Switch between cams and make sure nothing slips past you while you’re busy gaming. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209860/extras/501656dfc0f8a0ea661930294907dc1c.poster.avif?t=1737066645\" width=800 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209860/extras/501656dfc0f8a0ea661930294907dc1c.webm?t=1737066645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209860/extras/501656dfc0f8a0ea661930294907dc1c.mp4?t=1737066645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal is simple: beat the stages of the platformer to gain battery. But with everything happening around you, staying focused is easier said than done. Can you finish the game before something finishes you?</p>",
